<item>
            <title>[LU-3213] Interop 2.3.0&lt;-&gt;2.4 failure on test suite sanity-scrub test_11: (5) Expect 101 objects skipped, but got 107</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3213</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3ee8e86a-a7f9-11e2-ba78-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3ee8e86a-a7f9-11e2-ba78-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_11 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(5) Expect 101 objects skipped, but got 107&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;== sanity-scrub test 11: OI scrub skips the new created objects only once == 23:49:29 (1366267769)&lt;br/&gt;
stopall&lt;br/&gt;
setupall&lt;br/&gt;
total: 100 creates in 1.82 seconds: 54.93 creates/second&lt;br/&gt;
Started LFSCK on the MDT device lustre-MDT0000.&lt;br/&gt;
 sanity-scrub test_11: @@@@@@ FAIL: (5) Expect 101 objects skipped, but got 107 &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>client: 2.3.0&lt;br/&gt;
server: tag-2.3.64</environment>
